reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great bags for guys!
reviews.reviewText: I like these bags feels well made and plenty of room for all of my bathroom stuff that I don't like to leave laying around in there. The zipper is solid as is the strap to carry it with. I think they will last a long time so I'm not sure why they package so many of them together. I've already started using another one for a tool pouch, holding what ever tools I need for small jobs around the house. I'll eventually share some with friends I guess, but I really like them so I'll use them a lot.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bags, great value!
reviews.reviewText: These bags are very nice, especially for the value price and for so many of them.They are imitation leather, but have the pattern and look of saffiano leather, which I love.So many bags! Lol. I will need to find uses for all of them. Would be a great kit for bachelor or bachelorette favor kits. Or, for making toiletries kits for the homeless for the holidays.Great value and good quality. No complaints from me.
